{"tid":117081,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【一周必看】最美紅色女特工辭世　曾救周恩來脫臉","createTime":"2017-02-12T01:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T17:24:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3d29d654b690d3af1b38f87f6007dc4f7d95a56","tid":117081,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T01:56:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19925634&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19925634%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170212&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62P1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a494b416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19925634%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170212&h=8da1123b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19925634&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170212</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】最美紅色女特工辭世　曾救周恩來脫臉<br />\n<br />\n被譽為最美的紅色女特工黃慕蘭，周二在浙江杭州因病辭世，終年110歲。<br />\n<br />\n黃慕蘭出身湘中名門，北伐前夕成為婦女運動領袖，19歲就加入中共。國共決裂後被派赴上海任中共中央書記處秘書兼機要交通員，從事地下工作屢建奇功。她用美貌和魅力，曾救周恩來等中共領導於危難，被周讚為「黨百科全書」。一生傳奇至死未曾全部解密。<br />\n<br />\n《黃慕蘭自傳》/上海《澎湃新聞》/山東《半島晨報》<br />\n<br />\n上一則:&nbsp;【一周必看】原來普巴係講價高手？　十星期人工買新屋<br />\n<br />\n下一則:&nbsp;【一周必看】擱淺鯨魚成肚膠袋　塞爆腸道誰之過？"},{"pid":"70dee77f05f5cd3e1d47e97c390c24f7da1ac9dc","tid":117081,"uid":75755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dadfe789fd256e998f07798f2821b437a88915","tid":117081,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"110歲...<br />\n所以話，殺人放火金腰帶"},{"pid":"e3bab37264cc4907cdd57a3d04c64ced4a4c6243","tid":117081,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n幫中共乜柒乜柒<br />\n<br />\n人地話唔關你事又話你內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e3aa8dc142d821a6d890dfe09bdfe53f97b1f2","tid":117081,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n幫中共乜柒乜柒<br />\n<br />\n人地話唔關你事又話你內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n110歲乜都賺哂啦，仲抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913968eced1fee810b6a850008ecd86930361203","tid":117081,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:31:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n幫中共乜柒乜柒<br />\n<br />\n人地話唔關你事又話你內鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n110歲乜都賺哂啦，仲抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊佢坐左17碌"},{"pid":"20c0146f0b2d1a37cfb765d80e3dd784fc0f803b","tid":117081,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"萬人斬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}